participant_b.entity_text: Kv2.1 alpha-subunit of the I K  channel

verbose_text: We unexpectedly found that GDF15 did not decrease the I K or I A amplitude or protein expression in low K + / serum-free cultured CGNs; in contrast, GDF15 significantly increased the I K amplitude by enhancing the expression of the Kv2.1 alpha-subunit of the I K channel in immature CGNs.
evidence: expression of the Kv2.1 alpha-subunit of the I K  channel
